  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00277', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在大洋航行中決定電羅經誤差最精確的方法係為下列何者？', '["比較觀測天體的電羅經方位與觀測時間天體的計算方位", "比較電羅經艏向與標準羅經磁艏向", "比較電羅經航向與兩次天體定位間的實際航向", "因無法確定水流故在航行中無法得到電羅經誤差"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00278', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '本船航行中，雷達設定在相對運動顯示狀態，若目標回波維持靜止不動，則應屬於下列何種情境？', '["目標與本船航向相同", "目標與本船航速相同", "目標與本船航向及航速相同", "目標與本船航速相同但航向相反"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00279', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於行星運行的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["會合（Conjunction）指由太陽看行星與地球成一直線的情況", "內行星（Inferiorplanets）指水星、金星、地球與火星", "觀測金星最佳的時間是黎明前（啟明）或日落後（長庚）", "由地球看太陽與火星成一直線時，稱為外會合（Superiorconjunction）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00280', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某船L90公尺，浮面中心在船舯向後1.5公尺處，艏吃水4.50公尺，艉吃水5.00公尺，TPC10噸，MTC （orMCTC）120噸-公尺，若將450噸貨物裝於船舯向前14公尺處，則此次裝貨所產生的俯仰差變化量為何？', '["52.50公分（艏俯）", "58.13公分（艏俯）", "46.88公分（艉俯）", "55.38公分（艉俯）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00281', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '本船的磁羅經航向為145°，若得知當地磁差為3°E，又由自差表查得自差為5°W，則本船的真航向為何？', '["143°", "147°", "153°", "137°"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00282', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某船的船長150公尺，船寬20公尺，吃水5公尺，排水體積9000立方公尺，試求該船的方塊係數（Block Coefficient,C ）為何？ B', '["0.81", "0.72", "0.60", "0.52"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00283', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某船DR(60°N,072°W)，航向090°，航速20節；若太陽GHA291°，則請計算經過多少時間後，太陽恰通 過該船舶的天子午線？（提示：假設太陽每小時的時角變率15°）', '["3小時", "6小時", "9小時", "12小時"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('customs-f19eb2bd-moex-00284', 'customs-f19eb2bd', 'customs-f19eb2bd-moex-112-248a632e', 'sub-customs-f19eb2bd-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'A船航向（SH）為310°，測得B船相對方位（RB）為280°，若已知B船艏向（SH）030°，則B船測A 船之相對方位（RB）為何？', '["260°", "200°", "080°", "020°"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:22:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c6084d1518a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0de76f111bf0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "151", "s": "2006", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "航海船藝大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "customs", "civil_category": "船舶駕駛"}'::jsonb, NULL),
